OL,3,CLaw introduced to strengthen OBR and
OL,4,Cprevent repeat of Truss mini-budget
OL,6,FA new law forcing ministers to consult
OL,7,Fthe budget watchdog on major tax and
OL,8,Fspending changes will be introduced in
OL,9,Fthe Commons on Thursday.
OL,11,FThe Budget Responsibility Bill,
OL,12,Fannounced in the King's Speech, is
OL,13,Fdesigned to avoid a repeat of Liz
OL,14,FTruss's 2022 mini-budget which spooked
OL,15,Finvestors and sparked a run on the
OL,16,Fpound.
