OL,3,CLaw introduced to strengthen OBR and
OL,4,Cprevent repeat of Truss mini-budget
OL,6,FIf ministers seek to unveil such
OL,7,Fmeasures without asking for an OBR
OL,8,Fforecast, the watchdog can rule that
OL,9,Fthe "fiscal lock" has been triggered
OL,10,Fand publish a full fiscal forecast or
OL,11,Fassessment.
OL,13,FEmergency measures lasting fewer than
OL,14,Ftwo years, such as the response to the
OL,15,FCovid pandemic, will not require an
OL,16,Findependent OBR assessment.
