OL,6,FIn the City on Thursday, Chancellor
OL,7,FRachel Reeves will say that the law
OL,8,Fwill deliver economic stability, boost
OL,9,Fmarket confidence and protect family
OL,10,Ffinances.
OL,12,FShe said: "This Government's defining
OL,13,Fmission is to deliver economic growth.
OL,15,F"However, growth can only come through
OL,16,Feconomic stability and a commitment to
OL,17,Fsound public money so never again can
OL,18,Fa government play fast and loose with
OL,19,Fthe public finances.
