OL,6,F"This new law is part of our plan to
OL,7,Ffix the foundation of our economy so
OL,8,Fwe can rebuild Britain and make every
OL,9,Fpart of the country better off."
OL,11,FLouise Hellem, chief economist at the
OL,12,FCBI business group, said: "Ensuring
OL,13,Flarge changes in tax and spending
OL,14,Fpolicy are always subject to an
OL,15,Findependent assessment by the Office
OL,16,Ffor Budget Responsibility will give
OL,17,Fbusinesses and investors additional
OL,18,Fconfidence in the stability of the
OL,19,Fpublic finances."
