OL,6,FThe Bill ` one of the first from the
OL,7,FKing's Speech to be introduced ` comes
OL,8,Fless than two years after then-
OL,9,FConservative prime minister Ms Truss
OL,10,Fand her chancellor Kwasi Kwarteng's
OL,11,F#45 billion spree of unfunded tax cuts.
OL,13,FOne of the reasons the markets were so
OL,14,Fspooked by their mini-budget was that
OL,15,Fthe pair refused to publish the OBR's
OL,16,Findependent forecasts for the public
OL,17,Ffinances alongside the plans.
