OL,6,FIt said on Wednesday: "The 'fiscal
OL,7,Flock' is intended to capture and
OL,8,Fprevent those announcements that could
OL,9,Fresemble the disastrous Liz Truss
OL,10,F'mini-budget', announced on 23
OL,11,FSeptember 2022, which would have cost
OL,12,F#48 billion per year by 2027/28, and
OL,13,Fwas not subject to an OBR forecast and
OL,14,Fdamaged Britain's credibility with
OL,15,Finternational lenders."
